race.comment: SKATING ON BY (4) has returned in terrific order, showing grit to prevail here last time after racing on speed. Peaking now and aided by the claim, she can make it two on the bounce. SAMANTH (9) caught the eye fresh and backed it up with a brave chasing effort on speed at Clare. Also peaking now and shapes as a clear danger. STRAWBERRY SWING (11) disappointed last start but had excuses. Was a stylish winner when resuming at Clare and is a strong chance to atone if she rediscovers that form. MEG'S MAGIC (3) will get back from the draw but is worth watching late with her sharp finish. DIDWEWIN (12) will improve second-up, though will need some luck from the draw. Keeping safe.
